1948;;Saraband for Dead Lovers;;British;;Basil Dearden;;Joan Greenwood, Stewart Granger;;historical drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saraband_for_Dead_Lovers;;Sophie Dorothea (Joan Greenwood) seeks solace from dashing Count Philip Konigsmark (Stewart Granger) when her husband Prince George Louis (Peter Bull), later to become King George I of Great Britain, wants nothing to do with her. The lovers are brought down by a jealous Countess Platen (Flora Robson).